{"tid":1794144,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[NBA翻版] ESPN引央視消息：若奧斯爾不再上陣 將復播阿仙奴","createTime":"2019-12-23T01:59:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T14:35:58.000Z","uid":6103,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"b7cde8a8bcf48aca48cd41674fe9e8a75522caa6","tid":1794144,"uid":6103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T01:59:44.000Z","msg":"2019-12-23 HKT 08:12<br />\nESPN引述央視消息稱，若奧斯爾不再上陣，將復播阿仙奴的賽事。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n效力英超阿仙奴的德國球員奧斯爾，早前發表聲援中國新疆維吾爾人的言論之後，內地中央電視台取消直播阿仙奴對曼城的賽事。<br />\n<br />\n在過去星期六，阿仙奴主場與愛華頓賽和0:0的賽事，賽前公布的陣容中，未有包括奧斯爾。根據體育頻道ESPN報道，央視突然在網上直播這場賽事，只提供英語旁述。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述央視的消息指出，若果阿仙奴由今個星期四對般尼茅夫的賽事開始，不再派出奧斯爾上陣，央視將會繼續播放阿仙奴的賽事。<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴領隊龍格堡早前表示，奧斯爾未有被列入對愛華頓的賽事，因為狀態不足，以及上一場對曼城的賽事態度有問題。 <br />\n<br />\nsource : <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499117-20191223.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499117-20191223.htm&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwfG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=f5511212\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499117-20191223.htm&h=14329958\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499117-20191223.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n煲大佢，排陣出邊個都要問准共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d84878ca1ebb0f846574a44ee521c25dafec74","tid":1794144,"uid":8441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T02:01:59.000Z","msg":"懲罰緊邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9db421b82c050cddb5cbacedd791d4712c6715b","tid":1794144,"uid":13149,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T02:09:41.000Z","msg":"錢都照收 理撚得你播唔播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03521a4f29fa435eec4ce4eb73e0dd02d271c822","tid":1794144,"uid":53003,"like":1,"dislike"